description: King's Authentic Philly Cheesesteak is bringing Philly to the South making delicious Philly cheesesteak combinations. A couple from Philly decided to start making the sandwiches that offer both great flavors and cheesy satisfaction to anyone that consumes. The friendly service brings you in and the taste of a great Philly cheesesteak keeps you coming back!
name: King's Authentic Philly Cheesesteaks
